Richards Bay Minerals to Extend Mine Life, Business Day Reports

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-09T05:06:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-09/richards-bay-minerals-to-extend-mine-life-business-day-reports.html
Richards Bay Minerals Ltd., a South
African venture between  BHP Billiton Ltd. (BHP)  and  Rio Tinto Plc (RIO) ,
plans to extend the life of its Zulti South mining lease area
until about 2043 from 2030, Business Day reported, citing Joey
Kunji-Behari, general manager of mining and planning at RBM.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  